casebody.data:
DARRAH, Respondent, v. BOYS et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by James W. Darrah against James Boys and another.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and FOLLETT and PARKER, JJ.

A. T. Cushman, for appellants. C. C. Keeler, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
